OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy at
OL,6,Ffirst with plenty of showers through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight, locally
OL,8,Fheavy. Some clear spells developing in
OL,9,Fthe early hours, with a rural frost
OL,10,Fpossible. Brisk winds becoming
OL,11,Fconfined to the coast overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,14,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,15,Flocally heavy with hail and thunder.
OL,16,FFeeling rather cold, with temperatures
OL,17,Fbelow normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
